---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Factory & Plant 3D Scanning - Digital Twins for Manufacturing"
  description="Industrial 3D laser scanning for factories and manufacturing plants. Digital twins for smart manufacturing, process optimization, facility management."
  keywords="factory 3d scanning, plant digital twin, manufacturing laser scanning, industrial scanning"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Factory & Plant 3D Scanning</h1>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mb-8">Comprehensive facility documentation and digital twins for manufacturing plants. Trimble X12 and NavVis VLX3 for large industrial spaces.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold">Get Free Quote</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">Manufacturing Applications</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6"><strong>Factory Digital Twins:</strong> Complete 3D models for facility management</div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6"><strong>Process Optimization:</strong> Document workflows and layouts</div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6"><strong>Equipment Scanning:</strong> As-built documentation of machinery</div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6"><strong>Plant Retrofits:</strong> Scan-to-BIM for renovation projects</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>


